<p>Springfield residents have access to multiple layers of incentives for solar and HVAC upgrades. The federal solar Investment Tax Credit (ITC) provides a 30% tax credit for solar installations through 2032, making it an ideal time to invest. Massachusetts offers additional state incentives through the Solar Massachusetts Renewable Target (SMART) program, which provides performance-based incentives for solar production over 10-20 years.</p>

